Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.99,0:37:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉你我们做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll tell you what we've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.63,0:37:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们向凯蒂的牺牲致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've honored Katie's sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切皆由你女儿开始  艾伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This all started with your daughter, Alan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.61,0:37:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该感到自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should be proud.
