Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.30,0:38:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上到楼下来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you coming downstairs soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我们做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.97,0:39:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你留了剩菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.47,0:39:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道蛋奶酥可不可以再加热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not sure the souffle can reheat.
