Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.74,0:39:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟丹尼在实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Y... I was at the lab with Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后山姆来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then, uh, Sam came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.36,0:39:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不给我打电话  我很担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't you call me? I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不能  知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I couldn't, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.88,0:39:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.14,0:39:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是不能  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just couldn't. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.31,0:39:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还没准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're not ready to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.53,0:39:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你的经历  没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what's going on with you, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.66,0:39:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要时间  我可以等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you need time, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.78,0:39:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要自己一个人扛着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have to do this by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.39,0:40:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了  有我们在身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're here now. With us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.93,0:40:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.32,0:40:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你加热一盘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll heat you up a plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.17,0:40:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要知道你没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He-he needs to know you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.62,0:40:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.23,0:40:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你画了张画\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I drew you a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.93,0:40:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  可以给我看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did? Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.68,0:40:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把一家人放在飞船里  那样他们会安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I put the family in the spaceship, so that they'd be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.49,0:40:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Safe from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.87,0:40:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.99,0:40:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Extinction?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.01,0:40:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪里学到的这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where'd you learn about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.95,0:40:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去博物馆的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the museum today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.20,0:40:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是更强  更聪明的物种生存的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's where the stronger, smarter species survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.07,0:41:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我替你保守秘密了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's okay... I kept your secret.
